fields.title: This is an issue of type: Bug
fields.description: All users can create tickets. They can represent bugs, tasks, or improvements.

fields.title: This is an issue of type: Improvement
fields.description: Admins can add multiple tickets to one project. They can also perform CRUD on tickets.

fields.title: This is an issue of type: Task
fields.description: Each ticket can be given a list of tags and a single priority.
